description:
This is my favorite wonton place! I'm honestly at a loss for words by how good the wonton ho fun soup is. The noodles are so soft and chewy, wonton is juicy, big and flavorful and the soup itself has a hint of pepper making it a lil spicy. A great combo right there!

I also tried their chicken wings and it has MEAT in it not just bones. Crazy right?

Only reason I gave them 4 stars is because customers service. They're so rude and slow but the food is good so screw everything else (;
